s/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:34683:"\n<h2>Introduction</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The latest release of Connections added a new block for the WordPress Block editor, the Team Block.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a full featured block powered by Connections. This is not a &#8220;<em>lite</em>&#8221; version either. Similar premium plugins cost $20 or more but we have added this as a free feature available to <strong><em>all</em></strong> users!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Feature Highlights</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can choose between several layout options and layout style variations. Here&#8217;s a quick breakdown of those options:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Grid<ul><li>Clean</li><li>Flip</li><li>Slide</li><li>Overlay </li></ul></li><li>List<ul><li>Left</li><li>Right</li></ul></li><li>Table</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>If you choose the Grid or List layout you can choose whether or not to display a drop shadow. You can also choose to add a border and set its color and width.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In all Layout options / Style variations you can choose between a square image, a square image with rounded corners or a circle image. You can choose whether or not to add a border to the image and set its color and width.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All layout style variations are mobile ready!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Theme independant! The Team block will work in all the popular themes such as Avada, Divi, Enfold and OceanWP. Using the available style options the Team block can be tweaked to fit into most theme designs.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Examples</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The following examples are using the actual Team block. These are not mockups or screenshots!</p>\n\n\n\n<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>\n\n\n\n<h3>Grid :: Clean</h3>\n\n\n<style>\n#cn-team-container-38ddfdb5 {\n	grid-template-columns: repeat( 3, 1fr );\n	gap: 25px;\n}\n#cn-team-container-38ddfdb5 .cn-team-member {\n	border: 1px solid #BABABA;\n	border-radius: 12px;\n}\n#cn-team-container-38ddfdb5 .cn-team-member .cn-image {\n	border: 0px solid #BABABA !important;\n	border-radius: 0px !important;\n}\n</style><div class="cn-team-container cn-grid cn-columns-3 cn-card cn-clean cn-box-shadow" id="cn-team-container-38ddfdb5"><div class="cn-team-member">\n	<span class="cn-image-style"><span style="display: block; max-width: 100%; width: 600px"><img width="600" height="600" sizes="100vw" class="cn-image photo" alt="Photo of Byron M Adams" title="Photo of Byron M Adams" srcset="//connections-pro.com/wp-content/uploads/connections-images/byron-adams/ID-100202145-114f6aca83df43c2c9ab782d708bd908.jpg 1x"/></span></span>\n<span class="fn n notranslate"> <span class="given-name">Byron</span> <span class="additional-name">M</span> <span class="family-name">Adams</span> </span>\n<span class="title notranslate">Financial Planner</span>\n<span class="phone-number-block">\n	<span class="tel cn-phone-number cn-preferred cn-phone-number-preferred"><span class="value">803-463-7831</span><span class="type" style="display: none;">work</span></span>\n\n</span>\n<span class="email-address-block">\n	<span class="email cn-email-address cn-preferred cn-email-address-preferred"><span class="email-address"><span class="qrpelcg"><n pynff="inyhr" gvgyr="Oleba Nqnzf jbex rznvy." uers="znvygb:OlebaZNqnzf@wbheencvqr.pbz">OlebaZNqnzf@wbheencvqr.pbz</n></span><noscript><span style="unicode-bidi: bidi-override; direction:rtl;">mo&#99;&#46;ed&#105;p&#97;&#114;&#114;uo&#106;&#64;&#115;m&#97;&#100;AM&#110;&#111;&#114;yB</span></noscript></span><span class="type" style="display: none;">INTERNET</span></span>\n</span>\n</div>\n<div class="cn-team-member">\n	<span class="cn-image-style"><span style="display: block; max-width: 100%; width: 600px"><img width="600" height="600" sizes="100vw" class="cn-image photo" alt="Photo of Mary R Badgley" title="Photo of Mary R Badgley" srcset="//connections-pro.com/wp-content/uploads/connections-images/mary-